PEER
    - role: listen/stream audio files
    - platforms:
        - linux

    - features
        - announce: to send an announce of the LOCAL to the TRACKER
        - search: to search a song/album/artist/playlist/genre from a PROVIDER
        - stream: to stream from a PROVIDER
        - download: to download a song/album/playlist from PEER/PROVIDER
        - delete: to song/album/playlist delete from the LOCAL
        - contact: to send a feedback/request/report in the TRACKER
        - vote: to up/down vote

LOCAL
    - role: local node and its file system